# Placeholder so admin/server/ui/embed.go's `//go:embed all:dist` always
# has at least one file to embed, even before `make ui-build` runs.
#
# The FS() function in embed.go gates on index.html existing; this
# .gitkeep alone does not count as "the UI is built", so the server
# falls back to PlaceholderHTML at runtime.
#
# This file is intentionally force-added past .gitignore (which excludes
# **/dist/). Real build artifacts (index.html, assets/) remain ignored.
